<hr data-start="112" data-end="115">
<h3 data-start="117" data-end="165" data-section-id="vi08qr">✅ 🎯 Best Answer (HR + Technical – 1 minute)</h3>
<p data-start="167" data-end="288">“Hello, my name is Divesh Kumar. I am currently pursuing B.Tech in Computer Science from Poornima College of Engineering.</p>
<p data-start="290" data-end="519">I have hands-on experience in data analysis using SQL, Python, Power BI, and Excel. During my internship at Sharpener Tech, I worked on data cleaning, exploratory data analysis, and built dashboards to generate business insights.</p>
<p data-start="521" data-end="746">I have also worked on projects like an e-commerce SQL data analysis project, where I analyzed pricing, inventory, and revenue trends, and a Power BI dashboard project where I created interactive reports for sales forecasting.</p>
<p data-start="748" data-end="878">Additionally, I have experience using Python libraries like Pandas and Matplotlib to analyze customer behavior and visualize data.</p>
<p data-start="880" data-end="1037">I am passionate about turning raw data into meaningful insights and I am looking for an opportunity to apply my skills in a real-world business environment.”</p>
<hr data-start="1039" data-end="1042">
<h3 data-start="1044" data-end="1078" data-section-id="3njxbn">✅ 🔥 Short Version (30–40 sec)</h3>
<p data-start="1080" data-end="1185">“Hi, I’m Divesh Kumar, a Computer Science student with strong skills in SQL, Python, Power BI, and Excel.</p>
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1425">I have practical experience through projects and an internship where I performed data cleaning, analysis, and built dashboards. I’ve worked on an e-commerce SQL project and a Power BI sales dashboard project to generate business insights.</p>
<p data-start="1427" data-end="1518">I’m passionate about data analysis and eager to contribute to data-driven decision-making.”</p>
<hr data-start="1520" data-end="1523">
<h3 data-start="1525" data-end="1555" data-section-id="14drise">✅ 💡 Tips (Very Important)</h3>
<ul data-start="1557" data-end="1668">
<li data-start="1557" data-end="1585" data-section-id="5yzhha">
<p data-start="1559" data-end="1585">Speak <strong data-start="1565" data-end="1585">confident + slow</strong></p>
