<hr data-start="482" data-end="485">
<h3 data-start="487" data-end="533" data-section-id="c6xzeu">🔍 What this does (interview explanation):</h3>
<ul data-start="535" data-end="605">
<li data-start="535" data-end="589" data-section-id="7th0km">
<p data-start="537" data-end="589"><strong data-start="537" data-end="555">StandardScaler</strong> standardizes numerical features</p>
</li>
<li data-start="590" data-end="605" data-section-id="r6a0bf">
<p data-start="592" data-end="605">Formula used:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<span class="katex-display" style=""><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>Z</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>X</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>μ</mi></mrow><mi>σ</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Z = \frac{X - \mu}{\sigma}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.07153em;">Z</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 2.0463em; vertical-align: -0.686em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 1.3603em;"><span style="top: -2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.03588em;">σ</span></span></span><span style="top: -3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width: 0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top: -3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.07847em;">X</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">μ</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 0.686em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></span>
<ul data-start="641" data-end="704">
<li data-start="641" data-end="704" data-section-id="1jl22bn">
<p data-start="643" data-end="660">Converts data to:</p>
<ul data-start="663" data-end="704">
<li data-start="663" data-end="675" data-section-id="1dr4aiq">
<p data-start="665" data-end="675">Mean = 0</p>
</li>
<li data-start="678" data-end="704" data-section-id="1uyti64">
<p data-start="680" data-end="704">Standard deviation = 1</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="706" data-end="709">
<h3 data-start="711" data-end="743" data-section-id="sc7odk">🎯 Why scaling is important:</h3>
<ul data-start="745" data-end="896">
<li data-start="745" data-end="825" data-section-id="1e0s415">
<p data-start="747" data-end="825">Prevents large values (like mileage) dominating small ones (like engineSize)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="826" data-end="896" data-section-id="n3aw3g">
<p data-start="828" data-end="852">Improves performance of:</p>
<ul data-start="855" data-end="896">
<li data-start="855" data-end="876" data-section-id="14n5lqy">
<p data-start="857" data-end="876">Linear Regression</p>
</li>
<li data-start="879" data-end="886" data-section-id="16rb277">
<p data-start="881" data-end="886">KNN</p>
</li>
<li data-start="889" data-end="896" data-section-id="177qi1s">
<p data-start="891" data-end="896">SVM</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="898" data-end="901">
<h3 data-start="903" data-end="936" data-section-id="1h06fdc">⚠️ Important Interview Point:</h3>
<p data-start="938" data-end="958">👉 Not required for:</p>
<ul data-start="959" data-end="994">
<li data-start="959" data-end="976" data-section-id="1tr1ixq">
<p data-start="961" data-end="976">Decision Tree</p>
</li>
<li data-start="977" data-end="994" data-section-id="c8z6ga">
<p data-start="979" data-end="994">Random Forest</p>
</li>
</ul>
