<hr data-start="315" data-end="318">
<h1 data-start="320" data-end="354" data-section-id="1bqj0ue">🔍 Explanation (Interview Ready)</h1>
<h3 data-start="356" data-end="380" data-section-id="boy39l"><span role="text">✅ <strong data-start="362" data-end="380">accuracy_score</strong></span></h3>
<ul data-start="381" data-end="426">
<li data-start="381" data-end="426" data-section-id="k1tls6">
<p data-start="383" data-end="426">Measures how many predictions are correct</p>
</li>
</ul>
<span class="katex-display" style=""><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>t</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>P</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>T</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>l</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>P</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Accuracy = \frac{Correct\ Predictions}{Total\ Predictions}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.8778em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mord mathnormal">cc</span><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.03588em;">cy</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 2.0574em; vertical-align: -0.686em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 1.3714em;"><span style="top: -2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.13889em;">T</span><span class="mord mathnormal">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.01968em;">l</span><span class="mspace">&nbsp;</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.13889em;">P</span><span class="mord mathnormal">re</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="mord mathnormal">c</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="mord mathnormal">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span></span></span><span style="top: -3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width: 0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top: -3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mord mathnormal">orrec</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mspace">&nbsp;</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.13889em;">P</span><span class="mord mathnormal">re</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="mord mathnormal">c</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="mord mathnormal">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 0.686em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></span>
<hr data-start="493" data-end="496">
<h3 data-start="498" data-end="524" data-section-id="1ipbjpp"><span role="text">✅ <strong data-start="504" data-end="524">confusion_matrix</strong></span></h3>
<ul data-start="525" data-end="561">
<li data-start="525" data-end="561" data-section-id="1sqw2nr">
<p data-start="527" data-end="561">Shows actual vs predicted values</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="563" data-end="580">👉 Output format:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="581" data-end="609"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-f8sla627.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>[[TN  FP]</span><br><span> [FN  TP]]</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ul data-start="611" data-end="704">
<li data-start="611" data-end="633" data-section-id="ucth16">
<p data-start="613" data-end="633">TN = True Negative</p>
</li>
<li data-start="634" data-end="657" data-section-id="1iy3kmt">
<p data-start="636" data-end="657">FP = False Positive</p>
</li>
<li data-start="658" data-end="681" data-section-id="1xkjtb7">
<p data-start="660" data-end="681">FN = False Negative</p>
</li>
<li data-start="682" data-end="704" data-section-id="1t79e3w">
<p data-start="684" data-end="704">TP = True Positive</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="706" data-end="709">
<h3 data-start="711" data-end="742" data-section-id="1rt9610"><span role="text">✅ <strong data-start="717" data-end="742">classification_report</strong></span></h3>
<ul data-start="743" data-end="795">
<li data-start="743" data-end="795" data-section-id="12z8dl6">
<p data-start="745" data-end="751">Gives:</p>
<ul data-start="754" data-end="795">
<li data-start="754" data-end="767" data-section-id="128gcpq">
<p data-start="756" data-end="767">Precision</p>
</li>
<li data-start="770" data-end="780" data-section-id="q9g0jh">
<p data-start="772" data-end="780">Recall</p>
</li>
<li data-start="783" data-end="795" data-section-id="1pvuja2">
<p data-start="785" data-end="795">F1-score</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="797" data-end="832">👉 Very useful for model evaluation</p>
<hr data-start="834" data-end="837">
<h1 data-start="839" data-end="868" data-section-id="17qxihf">🎯 Interview Answer (Short)</h1>
<p data-start="870" data-end="1081">“I use accuracy_score to check overall correctness, confusion_matrix to understand prediction errors, and classification_report to evaluate precision, recall, and F1-score for better model performance analysis.”</p>
<hr data-start="1083" data-end="1086">
<p data-start="1088" data-end="1234" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want, I can:<br>
